COACH.estimation_method.ExpertOpinion.ExpertOpinion module¶

Example estimation method which captures expert opinion, i.e. it takes one parameter which is also the result of the estimation.

class COACH.estimation_method.ExpertOpinion.ExpertOpinion.ExpertOpinion[source]¶

Bases: COACH.framework.coach.EstimationMethod

This is a simple example of an estimation method. It takes one parameter, and just returns it.
